ExtDesc.message: Tabs tree, bookmarks and history in a highly configurable sidebar.

ActionTitle.message:
Toggle Sidebery sidebar
Middle click: Open settings

KbMenu.message: Open menu for selected (or active) tab, bookmark or panel

KbScrollToActivePanelTop.message: Scroll to the top of the active panel

KbScrollToActivePanelBottom.message: Scroll to the bottom of the active panel

KbGroupTabsAct.message: Group selected (or active) tabs and switch to group page

KbOpenNewTabInCurrPanel.message: Open a new tab in the active panel

KbOpenNewTabAfter.message: Open a new tab after the active tab

KbOpenNewTabAsFirstChild.message: Open a new tab as the first child of the active tab

KbOpenNewTabAsLastChild.message: Open a new tab as the last child of the active tab

KbRm.message: Close selected or active tab / Delete selected bookmarks

KbUnloadATIIP.message: Unload all tabs in inactive panels

KbActPrevActTabC.message: Activate previously active tab when clicking on the active tab (Tab flip)

KbActPanelPrevActTab.message: Active tabs history of panel: Back

KbActPanelNextActTab.message: Active tabs history of panel: Forward
